codelist.label: Type of Agri-Building Value
codelist.definition: The type of building, expressed as a code.
codelist.description: animal housing according to EU regulation (EC) 1200/2009 annex III chapter V, codes 5.01 - 5.03.99.

extensibility.label: Extensible with values at any level

value.label: 1_animal Housing
value.definition: A building to keep or to give shelter to animals

value.label: 2_storage
value.definition: A building to store products

value.label: 2_1_product Storage
value.definition: A building to store agriculural products, harvested products, animal feed.

value.label: 2_2_supplyStorage
value.definition: A building to store other products used in agri and aquaculture like chemicals, or fertilizers

value.label: 2_3_fuel Tank
value.definition: A tank to store fuel

value.label: 2_4_water Tank
value.definition: A tank to store water

value.label: 3_manure Storage And Treatment Facility
value.definition: A building to store and or treat manure

value.label: 3_1_manure Silo Solid Dug
value.definition: A silo to store solid dug

value.label: 3_2_manure Silo Liquid Manure
value.definition: a silo to store liquid manure

value.label: 3_3_manure Silo Slurry
value.definition: A silo to store slurry

value.label: 4_equipment Garage
value.definition: A building to park agriculure equipmetn and machinery

value.label: 5_technical Installation
value.definition: A building for technical installations

value.label: 6_mushrooms
value.definition: A building where mushrooms are grown

value.label: 7_greenhouse
value.definition: A building in which plants are grown (except mushrooms)

value.label: 8_shed
value.definition: A simple single story building , to provide shelter to animals, or to tore equipmetn or products.

value.label: 9_other
value.definition: Any other value not equal to one of the above listed values
